{"tid":109762,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"曾俊華：廿三條同政改可以一齊起步，目標2020年前完成到","createTime":"2017-02-06T07:39:27.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-06T13:57:55.000Z","uid":4661,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ae9686d770cd783b7aff05837c0cdf2457eaf306","tid":109762,"uid":4661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T07:39:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/01H936M.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F01H936M.jpg&h=2db8270e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"720e43b53819cc016daa1eb875361084e8441569","tid":109762,"uid":4661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T07:41:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20170206/56268347\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20170206%2F56268347&d=vUt%2FZqt5lAJzOS14TgBfpzA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=184091a6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20170206%2F56268347&h=b7df8655\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20170206/56268347</a><br />\n<br />\n【曾俊華政綱】831決定冇可能迴避 23條需讓具公信力法律人士參與<br />\n<br />\n特首參選人曾俊華周一下午舉行政綱發佈會，競選辦主任黎高穎怡及顧問李淑儀均有現身陪同回應記者提問。<br />\n<br />\n就政綱內提出重啟政改，曾俊華指政改是港人共同的期望，2014年時曾推行最終不成功，他重申如若能創造較和諧環境，與整個政治光譜人士有溝通，可以拿到好的共識，他會將討論結果如實讓中央知道，認為屆時中央會有準確判斷，並會盡快啟動政改五部曲，他又形容831是人大常委建立，會以此為基礎，「冇可能迴避」。<br />\n曾俊華又指出，23條立法是憲制責任，形容回歸以來未做到「係可惜」，他相信在推行內容和程序上可做得更好，他會先做一個白紙草案，讓具公信力的法律界人士參與製作內容，並以透明程序進行對話。"},{"pid":"03628b9a14488d9bfd98956fe6f79f332b44cd61","tid":109762,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T08:03:07.000Z","msg":"23條<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f15e32aac630b72e633228244629aa8ac60e9bc","tid":109762,"uid":64744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T08:04:32.000Z","msg":"如果係一換一<br />\n個人覺得可以考慮吖至少"},{"pid":"e63c2371d2e0e080716b2423c7bf05738bfec80e","tid":109762,"uid":58099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T12:47:01.000Z","msg":"。"},{"pid":"d9f16b3e98edb90d5081168b062ac42ed36d54ab","tid":109762,"uid":24140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T12:53:08.000Z","msg":"23條仲要831 方案下既普選<br />\n你要埋我果份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"524e33050f26cbb985b93f591684b5a3efb094a9","tid":109762,"uid":45518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T12:54:53.000Z","msg":"2020一次過食哂兩舊屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0cd81c8f687f8dc910d2d4c2ad6a194e24b0a23f","tid":109762,"uid":2795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T12:58:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果係一換一<br />\n個人覺得可以考慮吖至少</blockquote><br />\n同831一樣 咁當初做咁多為乜"},{"pid":"cc66071571a9b0712f98a0f1782bbb9d53e5452e","tid":109762,"uid":31,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T13:12:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果係一換一<br />\n個人覺得可以考慮吖至少</blockquote><br />\n你係咪痴撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1587fbf2508f6671ebf29fbad062772994efb919","tid":109762,"uid":40839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T13:14:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>如果係一換一<br />\n個人覺得可以考慮吖至少</blockquote><br />\n同831一樣 咁當初做咁多為乜</blockquote><br />\n接受831既話當初就過撚左啦<br />\n仲要無綁埋23條<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce503bd416bf2cf1533795d872d3d70753cb7df0","tid":109762,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T13:38:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96049e6958820f8eeb599ea9e56ef065b233219e","tid":109762,"uid":58099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T13:57:55.000Z","msg":"。"}]}